{"title":"王大嫂包饺子","authors":["张宪彬"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"王大嫂包饺子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张宪彬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员今天度假日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王大哥张罗去看戏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大嫂一人留下管食堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王大哥问她准备什么好吃的？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“放假日子吃好的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肉馅饺子，薄薄的皮。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王大哥摇头不相信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说大嫂吹牛皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一个人能包出五千饺子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骡子也能产双驹。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俱乐部里好热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快板，双簧，京评剧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精彩表演无心看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥心里打主意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“恩爱不过是夫妻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我得帮她包饺子。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脚迈进厨房里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥一看来了气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大嫂盘腿炕上坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消消停停看书呢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥数落她不理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从从容容下了地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锅里添满清泉水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回手打开吹风机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水花翻滚锅烧开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大嫂搬出一个木玩艺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手握木把摇三摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这东西又剁馅子又擀皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饺子自动往锅里跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大哥看得入了迷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边看来一边忙称赞："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“妇女可真了不起。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大嫂瞪了他一眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门缝瞧人，看扁俺妇女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们男子能闹革新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们妇女也能造机器。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}